声波小精灵 (Sound-Wave Sprite) pet feature
  The interaction rule engine (conditions → filters(operator/value) →
  actions, priority sort, cooldown, conditionWindowMs, stopOnMatch,
  stateful enter/exit with continuous mouse-move sustain) is PORTED and
  ADAPTED from:

    duzexu/desktop-pet
    https://github.com/duzexu/desktop-pet
    Copyright (C) duzexu — licensed under the GNU General Public License v3.0.

  Adaptations made for SoundVault:
    - Removed the asset/material sprite layer; the pet is rendered as a
      procedural audio-reactive canvas sprite (original SoundVault code).
    - Replaced desktop-pet action types (playAnimation / openPanel /
      pomodoro / disableInteractions / changeDisplay) with SoundVault
      equivalents (playSpriteAnim / openPetSettings / changeDisplay).
    - Added audio-linkage events (audioStart / audioLevel / audioStop)
      so the sprite reacts to SoundVault playback.

  Per the GPL-3.0, the adapted source retains the above attribution and
  is distributed under the same license.
